      "x": 1315, "y": 994,
      "width": 415, "height": 105,
      "text": "roster/{butler-name}/\n├── MANIFESTO.md       public identity & purpose\n├── CLAUDE.md          butler personality / system prompt\n├── AGENTS.md          runtime agent notes\n├── butler.toml        identity, schedule, modules config\n├── api/               router.py + models.py (optional)\n├── .agents/skills/    skill scripts (SKILL.md per skill)\n└── .claude -> .agents Claude Code compatibility symlink",
      "originalText": "roster/{butler-name}/\n├── MANIFESTO.md       public identity & purpose\n├── CLAUDE.md          butler personality / system prompt\n├── AGENTS.md          runtime agent notes\n├── butler.toml        identity, schedule, modules config\n├── api/               router.py + models.py (optional)\n├── .agents/skills/    skill scripts (SKILL.md per skill)\n└── .claude -> .agents Claude Code compatibility symlink",
